/* ============================================================================
   AI STACK CATALOG  —  this is your data + referral layer.
   ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
   This is the ONE file you'll edit most. To add a tool, copy a block below,
   paste it, and change the fields. To monetize, replace each "url" with YOUR
   affiliate / referral tracking link from the program named in "affiliate".

   FIELD GUIDE
     id          : unique short slug (no spaces)
     name        : display name
     category    : short human label shown on the card
     tags        : which USE-CASE domains this tool serves. MUST match the
                   domain ids in scoring.js (sales, marketing, support,
                   knowledge, docs, automation, data, hr, finance, itdev,
                   meetings). A tool can serve several.
     desc        : one-line "what it does"
     sizes       : company sizes it fits: 'small' (1-50), 'mid' (51-500),
                   'large' (500+)
     priceTier   : 'free' | 'low' | 'mid' | 'high'  (used for budget matching)
     hasFreePlan : true if there's a free plan (not just a trial)
     price       : human-readable starting price
     ease        : setup difficulty 1 (no-code/instant) .. 3 (needs tech help)
     affiliate   : the referral/affiliate program & network (or "None")
     commission  : rough payout — ALWAYS verify the live rate when you sign up
     url         : the link the "Try it" button uses  ->  PUT YOUR AFFILIATE
                   LINK HERE. For now it points at the vendor's site.
     site        : vendor homepage (reference)
   ========================================================================== */

