    tags:["sales", "meetings"],
    desc:"ZoomInfo-owned call recording and deal insights for revenue teams.",
    longDesc:"Revenue teams pick Chorus.ai for call recording and deal insights, and it's the natural choice if you already run ZoomInfo, which owns it. Strong at surfacing what's said across deals. Watch-out: enterprise custom pricing and Gong is widely seen as the sharper standalone product. Alternatives: Gong for the category lead, Avoma for SMB budgets.",
