    desc:"AI product manager that runs standups, follow-ups, and decisions in Slack/Telegram with transparent, source-linked memory.",
    longDesc:"Product and ops teams look at Cleo as an AI project manager that runs standups, follow-ups, and decisions in Slack or Telegram with source-linked memory. Appealing for lightweight, transparent team coordination. Watch-out: newer tool with unconfirmed pricing — verify reliability and data handling before depending on it. Alternatives: Standuply or Geekbot for async standups, Linear or Asana for actual project tracking.",
