    desc:"Project tool with AI for tasks, docs, and meeting notes.",
    longDesc:"Picked by teams already living in ClickUp who want AI woven into tasks, docs, and meeting notes rather than a separate tool. The draw is bundling — search, summaries, and automation across work you already track there. Watch-out: ClickUp's core app is famously feature-dense, so onboarding is a real cost. Alternatives: Notion AI for cleaner docs, Asana for simpler PM.",
