    tags:["itdev"],
    desc:"Autonomous coding agent for VS Code.",
    longDesc:"Developers pick Cline, a free open-source agent for VS Code, to autonomously plan and execute multi-file coding tasks with your choice of model and API key. Strong for agentic coding without subscription lock-in. Watch-out: bring-your-own-API costs and the usual need to review autonomous edits. Alternatives: Cursor for a polished editor, Claude Code for terminal work, Roo Code as a fork, Copilot for the mainstream.",
