    desc:"AI calendar that optimizes focus time and meetings.",
    longDesc:"Individuals and teams drowning in meetings pick Clockwise to auto-rearrange calendars and protect focus time. Strong, low-cost, and it works quietly in the background. Watch-out: it shines mainly for Google Calendar and dense meeting cultures; light users won't notice much. Alternatives: Reclaim.ai as the closest rival, Motion for AI task-plus-calendar planning.",
