    longDesc:"CRM picked specifically by outbound sales teams that live on the phone — built-in dialer is the differentiator. Affordable for SMB; pricing scales with seats. Watch-out: niche fit — if your sales motion is inbound or PLG, this is the wrong tool. Alternative: HubSpot for inbound, Salesforce for enterprise.",
