    tags:["sales", "data"],
    desc:"GDPR-friendly prospect data with mobile numbers and intent.",
    longDesc:"Mid-market and enterprise sales teams, especially in Europe, pick Cognism for GDPR-friendly prospect data with strong mobile-number coverage and intent. Best when EU compliance and phone-verified numbers matter. Watch-out: custom pricing and US coverage trails ZoomInfo. Alternatives: ZoomInfo for US depth, Apollo for value, Lusha for quick extension lookups.",
