    tags:["meetings", "knowledge"],
    desc:"UX research repository with AI tagging.",
    longDesc:"UX research teams pick Condens to store, tag, and search research data in one repository, with AI speeding up transcription and tagging. Strong as a focused research repo. Watch-out: niche and per-seat, so it's overkill if you only run occasional studies. Alternatives: Dovetail for a broader insights platform, EnjoyHQ or Notion for lighter needs.",
