    tags:["knowledge"],
    desc:"Team wiki with Atlassian Intelligence AI summaries and Q&A.",
    longDesc:"Teams already on Atlassian pick Confluence as their wiki, now with Atlassian Intelligence for summaries and natural-language Q&A across pages. Strong for documentation that lives next to Jira, with a free tier. Watch-out: it can become a sprawling, stale page graveyard without upkeep, and the AI needs a paid plan. Alternatives: Notion for a friendlier all-rounder, Guru for verified knowledge, Slite for simplicity.",
