    desc:"Open-source AI code assistant for VS Code and JetBrains.",
    longDesc:"Developers pick Continue.dev, an open-source assistant for VS Code and JetBrains, to wire in any model and customize their AI coding setup. Strong for teams wanting control, self-hosting, and model freedom for free. Watch-out: more configuration than turnkey tools, and you bring your own model costs. Alternatives: Cline for autonomous agents, Cursor for polish, Copilot for the mainstream, Tabnine for privacy.",
