    tags:["marketing", "sales"],
    desc:"AI copywriter and go-to-market workflows for marketing and sales teams.",
    longDesc:"Cheaper Jasper alternative aimed at SMB marketing and sales — useful for cold outreach sequences and GTM workflows. Free tier exists; Pro at $49/mo is the working setup. Watch-out: outputs need editing before they're send-worthy; treat it as a first-draft engine. Alternative: Jasper for brand-heavy teams, ChatGPT for cheaper general use.",
