    desc:"Multi-agent orchestration framework with enterprise tier.",
    longDesc:"Developers pick CrewAI to orchestrate multiple AI agents into role-based crews that collaborate on tasks, with both open-source and enterprise tiers. Strong for structured multi-agent workflows with less boilerplate than raw frameworks. Watch-out: still a developer tool with a learning curve and fast-changing APIs. Alternatives: AutoGen for Microsoft's approach, LangGraph for fine-grained state control.",
