    desc:"AI-first code editor that writes and edits code from natural language.",
    longDesc:"AI-first IDE — picked by engineers who want AI deeper than autocomplete: full file edits, multi-file refactors, agent mode. $20/seat/mo. Watch-out: VS Code fork — loses the \"stay in your existing editor\" advantage Copilot has. Alternative: Copilot for VS Code stay-put, Windsurf for similar IDE-replacement.",
