    tags:["marketing"],
    desc:"Behavioral messaging across email, push, in-app with AI optimization.",
    longDesc:"Product-led and B2C teams pick Customer.io for behavioral messaging across email, push, and in-app, triggered by real-time event data with AI optimization. Strong for sophisticated, data-driven lifecycle campaigns. Watch-out: it expects clean event data and technical setup, and pricing scales up. Alternatives: Braze or Iterable for enterprise, Klaviyo for ecommerce, Customer.io shines for SaaS.",
