    tags:["support", "marketing"],
    desc:"Live chat, automations, and AI for SaaS support.",
    longDesc:"SaaS teams pick Customerly for live chat, automations, and AI support in one affordable package with a free tier. Strong value for small support and marketing teams. Watch-out: smaller ecosystem and integrations than the incumbents. Alternatives: Intercom for the full platform, Crisp for cheap chat, HubSpot if you want CRM-attached support.",
