    longDesc:"Data and ML teams pick Databricks as a lakehouse unifying data engineering, analytics, and AI — with Mosaic AI and natural-language Genie for BI. Strong for large-scale data plus ML in one platform. Watch-out: powerful but complex and costly, needing skilled engineers. Alternatives: Snowflake for warehouse-first analytics, Google BigQuery, or a modular open-source stack.",
