    tags:["data"],
    desc:"Enterprise generative AI and ML platform.",
    longDesc:"Enterprises pick Dataiku as a collaborative platform for analytics, ML, and generative AI that serves both coders and no-code business analysts. Strong for operationalizing data science across mixed-skill teams. Watch-out: enterprise custom pricing and a real platform commitment. Alternatives: DataRobot for AutoML focus, Databricks for the lakehouse, Knime for an open-source option.",
