    longDesc:"Mid-market and enterprise support teams pick Decagon for autonomous AI agents that resolve customer issues across chat, email, and voice — not just deflect. Strong as a well-funded leader in agentic customer service. Watch-out: enterprise custom pricing and setup to safely automate real resolutions. Alternatives: Sierra as a close rival, Intercom Fin for a faster start, Ada or Forethought.",
