    tags:["sales", "docs"],
    desc:"AI sales agents that research, draft, and send personalized outbound at scale.",
    longDesc:"Outbound sales teams pick Regie.ai to let AI agents research prospects, draft personalized messages, and send at scale, freeing reps from manual sequencing. Strong for high-volume outbound. Watch-out: needs guardrails and review or it produces spammy, generic outreach that burns domains. Alternatives: Outreach for full sales engagement, 11x or AiSDR for AI-SDR rivals.",
