    tags:["itdev"],
    desc:"Build, host, and deploy apps in the browser with an AI agent.",
    longDesc:"Browser-based dev environment with AI Agent — picked by hobbyists, students, and shipping-fast teams who want code-to-deploy in one tab. Free tier covers learning; paid plans needed for serious work. Watch-out: not a serious production environment for medium-complexity apps. Alternative: Cursor for desktop AI coding, Bolt for similar.",
