    tags:["automation", "itdev"],
    desc:"Build internal apps and workflows fast, with AI assist.",
    longDesc:"Developers and technical ops teams pick Retool to build internal tools and admin apps fast, dragging components onto a canvas and wiring them to any database or API, with AI assist. Strong for replacing hacky internal scripts. Watch-out: per-seat pricing climbs and you still need some coding. Alternatives: Appsmith or Budibase for open-source, Airtable for lighter needs.",
