    tags:["sales", "support", "marketing"],
    desc:"AI layer across Sales, Service, and Marketing Clouds for forecasting and copy.",
    longDesc:"Makes sense almost exclusively for orgs already standardized on Salesforce, who want forecasting, summaries, and copy generated natively against their CRM data. The value is proximity to your data, not the AI itself. Watch-out: a $50/seat add-on on top of already-significant Salesforce costs. Alternative: HubSpot's built-in AI if you're on that stack instead.",
