    tags:["sales", "meetings"],
    desc:"Cadences, conversation intelligence, and forecasting in one platform.",
    longDesc:"Direct competitor to Outreach with similar features and slightly different UX preferences — pick comes down to which sales ops team prefers and which integrates better with your stack. The Rhythm AI signal layer is the recent differentiator. Watch-out: same scale and overhead as Outreach — not a tool to buy lightly. Alternative: Outreach, Apollo for cheaper SMB tier.",
