    tags:["knowledge"],
    desc:"Smart citation index that shows whether claims are supported.",
    longDesc:"Researchers and academics pick Scite.ai to see whether a claim is supported, contrasted, or mentioned by citing papers — citation context, not just counts. Strong for evaluating how a finding has held up. Watch-out: a focused research tool, not a general assistant, at a flat monthly price. Alternatives: Consensus for evidence Q&A, Elicit for synthesis, Semantic Scholar for free citation data.",
