    desc:"Real-time contact and company search with credits-based pricing.",
    longDesc:"Sales teams pick Seamless.ai for real-time contact and company search on a credits model. Best when you need to build lists quickly. Watch-out: data accuracy draws frequent complaints and users report aggressive auto-renewals — read the contract. Alternatives: Apollo for better value, ZoomInfo for depth, UpLead for verified accuracy.",
